      • parse

        public final void parse(java.lang.String message)
        receives a String and fires the apropiate Event. This method receives a String from the socket and then determines the correct event / action to be taken.
        Parameters:
        message - the message to be evaluated.

      • handleConnection

        private void handleConnection(Message msg)
        handles the connection messages. NICK : when the client changes its nickname -> inform via chat, replace in hashmap PONG : send by the server to test the connection, is disabled TOUT : connection timeout -> inform via chat FAIL : connection broken -> return to SelectServer EXIT : connection closed by server or client -> return to SelectServer
        Parameters:
        msg - the message

      • handleNickChange

        private void handleNickChange(Message msg)
        handles if a user changes his nickname or joins.
        Parameters:
        msg - the message with the nickchange.

      • handleGame

        private void handleGame(Message msg)
        messages for the game. implemented: QUIT : a player leaves the game GAME : actual status of a game JOIN : a player has joined a game
        Parameters:
        msg - the message

      • handleLobby

        private void handleLobby(Message msg)
        All messages concerning the Lobby / userstatus. implemented: QUIT : a user has quit the lobby JOIN : a user has joined the lobby -> announce in chat
        Parameters:
        msg - the message
